# 2 - To see usefull documentation on each function in this library: "bash _rtd_library --devhelp"



#::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
#::::::::::::::                                          ::::::::::::::::::::::
